8 AS INTRODUCED
9 An Act relating to nuisance; amending 50 O.S. 2021,
Section 21, which relates to certain unlawful acts;
10 modifying provisions related to actions resulting in
certain felony convictions; providing for certain
11 unlawful acts as nuisance; and providing an effective
date.
12
13 BE IT ENACTED BY THE PEOPLE OF THE STATE OF OKLAHOMA:
14 SECTION 1. AMENDATORY 50 O.S. 2021, Section 21, is
15 amended to read as follows:
16 Section 21. The repeated use of any real property or structure
17 thereon to commit unlawful drug distribution, prostitution, or human
18 and/or sex trafficking acts which result in a felony conviction
19 under the Oklahoma Uniform Controlled Dangerous Substances Act may
20 shall constitute a public nuisance.
21 SECTION 2. This act shall become effective November 1, 2025.
